Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超音學園三年級學生莫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家已經知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.11,0:01:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是她跟一位神秘少年遇上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼?你沒有帶卡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹人著急呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過念力球嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的小孩是玩這些嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的小孩...你也是個小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已50歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生於1980年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55\fad(200,200)\pos(480,680)}妖魔兵器!從過去來到的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，不是\N究竟到了哪裡去?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有妖魔反應，看來找對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今次有什麼陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:03:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開那些小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達基尼，撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要妖魔兵器完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們便再敵不過我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔兵器?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，想逃嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍是些卑鄙的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟他們做了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找相片中的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相片?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小孩是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是美夢妮叫我們去找的那個小孩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖有重病，但從醫院逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後也要照顧小孩\N真不夠運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如走進學校的話便幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是戀人的相片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這男孩是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事要辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，真兒 你如在街上\N見到這男孩便告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他離家出走了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣，拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然拜託我了就沒法推辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，還未發現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到還回來幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要找出這叫志郎的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如沒有他\N妖魔兵器便不能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎辦才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼?真遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟從何而來?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天對什麼感到為難?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道朋友現在的地址
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫志郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木笑真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼找高見裕次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著是本間鷹男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?\N你在找爺爺的朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也死了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1999年\N在我出生前發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那開始東京便一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所找的人，定是在那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?\N諾斯達姆的預言說中了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉竟跟那傢伙一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是...要告訴老師才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是電影嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最新的體驗電影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的什麼也不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因我睡下來是在1990年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡下來?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一段長時間的睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?真的沒事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你替我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟說謊似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能相信嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說已睡了四十年\N難以置信的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何要跑?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人要抓我，所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和說的一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老師要找的那離家出走的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找志郎什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉，讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，老師你們很古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別給我添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放有很多我那時代的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遊戲機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只對我們說\N去找一位重病的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但妖魔卻也在找同一個少年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夢妮\N究竟那少年是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志郎身體被病毒入侵\N懷著重病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的醫學\N或現今也醫不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他生於1980年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從10歲發病後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以冷凍睡眠\N不增加歲數的保管著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄望未來的科學\N能醫好那重病
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他父母懷著這樣的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣過了四十年，然而就在兩天前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志郎的維生艙被某人打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖魔嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還沒有治療志郎的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不快把他放回維生艙作冷凍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在數小時後便會死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易在冷凍睡眠中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻要再進入長眠，有點可憐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避我們也是這個緣故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不想再次進入冷凍睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了志郎著想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為何妖魔要捉他呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為志郎他...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還相信我是在1990年睡著的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你做的嗎?超能力?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉也一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉，現在的心情怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志郎，沒事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的站好，小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快點找到志郎和莫莉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高亞地區有妖魔出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是利用了志郎的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和所想的一樣\N是厲害的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼，感謝你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄成一團糟呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過份了\N被拿來當作是妖魔機械的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家去吧!\NBorg Get On!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷電，衝過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操控的是妖魔人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如將那傢伙收拾的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超音子彈無效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利斯，積克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使出三重攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會連志郎也一併擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用超級雷電的發射系統
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我射過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射到那傢伙的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?身體會撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，拜託了，只能這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積克，去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷電，把積克射出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能辦到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開那小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:18:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我被切開也不會放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Get On!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志郎...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再見...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我從冷凍睡眠醒來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到現在這時代\N也不能醫好我的病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道可能要\N再多睡數十數百年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我不想再睡了\N就算死了也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避妖魔和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但遇上付出性命來保護我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超音戰士和莫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有活下來的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算再多賭一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年再次睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他來說2030年的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能像是長眠中所做的短暫的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我們可能都是他夢中\N所見到的人也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼對莫莉說才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
